{"text_id":40553,"tokens":["Hypo","thyroidism"," is"," a"," condition"," where"," the"," thyroid"," gland"," in"," your"," body"," produces"," too"," little"," thyroid"," hormone","."," This"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," variety"," of"," symptoms",","," some"," of"," which"," can"," be"," subtle"," and"," difficult"," to"," spot","."," It","'","s"," important"," to"," be"," aware"," of"," the"," early"," signs"," of"," hypo","thyroidism"," so"," that"," you"," can"," seek"," treatment"," before"," the"," condition"," wors","ens","."," In"," this"," article",","," we","'","ll"," discuss"," how"," to"," spot"," early"," signs"," of"," hypo","thyroidism","."," ","\n","Method"," ","1",":"," Evaluate"," your"," energy"," levels",".","\n","One"," of"," the"," most"," common"," signs"," of"," potential"," hypo","thyroidism"," is"," fatigue",","," and","/","or"," a"," recent"," drop"," in"," your"," energy"," levels","."," You"," may"," feel"," tired"," even"," after"," getting"," a"," good"," night","'","s"," sleep",","," struggle"," to"," concentrate",","," or"," feel"," weak"," and"," sluggish"," throughout"," the"," day","."," ","\n","Method"," ","2",":"," Observe"," any"," recent"," weight"," changes",".","\n","Hypo","thyroidism"," may"," also"," cause"," you"," to"," gain"," weight",","," again"," because"," your"," metabolism"," is"," slowed"," down"," below"," its"," normal"," level","."," You"," may"," notice"," that"," you","'","ve"," gained"," weight"," despite"," not"," making"," any"," significant"," changes"," to"," your"," diet"," or"," exercise"," routine","."," ","\n","Method"," ","3",":"," Notice"," how"," you"," feel"," in"," the"," cold",".","\n","Another"," potential"," consequence"," of"," hypo","thyroidism"," is"," an"," intolerance"," of"," cold"," weather",","," meaning"," that"," you"," feel"," less"," able"," to"," handle"," being"," out"," in"," the"," cold","."," You"," may"," find"," yourself"," reaching"," for"," an"," extra"," blanket"," or"," layer"," of"," clothing"," even"," when"," others"," around"," you"," seem"," comfortable","."," ","\n","Method"," ","4",":"," Consider"," any"," changes"," in"," your"," skin",","," hair",","," or"," eyes",".","\n","Hypo","thyroidism"," can"," lead"," to"," signs"," such"," as"," drier",","," thicker"," skin"," (","from"," the"," glycos","amin","ogly","can"," deposits"," in"," your"," tissues",");"," a"," lack"," of"," sweating"," (","due"," to"," decreased"," metabolism",");"," fewer",","," coarser"," hairs"," on"," your"," body"," or"," eyebrows",";"," and","/","or"," brittle"," nails","."," You"," may"," also"," notice"," that"," your"," eyes"," appear"," puffy"," or"," swollen","."," ","\n","Method"," ","5",":"," Watch"," for"," changes"," in"," your"," mood"," or"," sleep"," habits",".","\n","For"," some",","," hypo","thyroidism"," can"," manifest"," as"," a"," depressed"," mood","."," You"," may"," feel"," irritable"," or"," have"," trouble"," sleeping",","," even"," if"," you"," previously"," had"," no"," difficulty"," with"," these"," issues","."," ","\n","Method"," ","6",":"," Take"," note"," of"," unusual"," constipation",".","\n","Hypo","thyroidism"," can"," also"," lead"," to"," constipation","."," You"," may"," notice"," that"," you","'","re"," having"," difficulty"," passing"," stools",","," or"," that"," you","'","re"," having"," bowel"," movements"," less"," frequently"," than"," usual","."," ","\n","Method"," ","7",":"," Be"," aware"," of"," any"," unusual"," shortness"," of"," breath",".","\n","Sometimes"," hypo","thyroidism"," can"," cause"," you"," to"," be"," short"," of"," breath",","," particularly"," during"," exertion","."," You"," may"," feel"," win","ded"," after"," climbing"," a"," flight"," of"," stairs"," or"," walking"," a"," short"," distance","."," ","\n","Method"," ","8",":"," Be"," on"," the"," lookout"," for"," other"," potential"," signs",".","\n","Hypo","thyroidism"," can"," manifest"," in"," a"," variety"," of"," different"," ways",","," and"," varies"," from"," person"," to"," person","."," Other"," potential"," signs"," to"," watch"," for"," include"," joint"," pain",","," muscle"," weakness",","," and"," heavy"," or"," irregular"," periods"," in"," women","."," ","\n","If"," you","'","re"," experiencing"," any"," of"," these"," symptoms",","," it","'","s"," important"," to"," speak"," with"," your"," doctor","."," They"," can"," help"," you"," determine"," whether"," hypo","thyroidism"," or"," another"," underlying"," condition"," is"," to"," blame",","," and"," work"," with"," you"," to"," develop"," a"," treatment"," plan","."," With"," proper"," care",","," you"," can"," manage"," hypo","thyroidism"," and"," feel"," like"," yourself"," again","."],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}